main event: A report of an unidentified flying object sighted in Christiansburg, Ohio, with insufficient data for evaluation.
interesting points: The report concluded that there was insufficient data for a scientific evaluation., The UFO was reported as a glowing light that moved erratically and silently., The sighting duration was reported to be between 10 to 15 minutes., The document included a request for detailed information from the witness., The observation was made in February 1967 and referred to an earlier unidentified observation.
sighted object: glowing light moving erratically in the sky
